On Fedora 13:

- Install GHC 7.0.2 (x86_64): http://haskell.org/ghc/dist/7.0.2/ghc-7.0.2-x86_64-unknown-linux.tar.bz2

    ./configure
    sudo make install

- Install Haskell Platfrom: http://lambda.galois.com/hp-tmp/2011.2.0.0/haskell-platform-2011.2.0.0.tar.gz

    ./configure
    make
    sudo make install

- Update cabal:

    cabal update

- Install dependencies:

    cabal install logict split fgl

- Build project:

    cabal clean && cabal configure && cabal build

- Run project:

    ./3color [GRAPH FILE]
